high_descs: Turn around towards the fridge and open it.
Take out the plum from the fridge.
Close the fridge, turn right to take one step towards the sink, and then turn right to face the microwave.
Place the plum inside the microwave to warm it up and take the plum out.
Turn right towards the wall, and then turn right towards the green bin on the floor.
Place the plum inside the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place the warmed plum inside the green bin.

high_descs: Turn left and move to the fridge.
Open the fridge and take out the brown egg behind the mug and apple on the top shelf.
Move a few feet to the left to the microwave.
Cook the egg in the microwave for a few seconds and take it back out.
Turn around and move to the green trash can across the room n the corner next to the stove.
Throw the egg away in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw a cooked egg in the trash can.

high_descs: Take the potato out of the fridge.
Bring the potato to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Bring the potato to the green trash can.
Put the potato in the green trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the green trash can.
